text: Xiangyangjie () is a subdistrict and the seat of Jinshi City in Hunan, China. The subdistrict was formed in 1966,the history of Wuling Town, according to the Dictionary of Chinese Administrative Divisions (中国行-政区划大典) published by the People's Publishing House of Zhejiang (浙江人民出版社) in December 2002, Yangyou Township () was merged to it. It has an area of with a population of about 20,440 (as of 2016).
